reviewText: this is only a 4 min video I am very unhappy with this purchase. it would have been nice to know I was buyin a commercial and not a full workout video. I like Denise Austin but feel this is a rip off.

In this workout you get a full bodyworkout using weights and a stepper. Denise Austin really makes you workout, and at the same time not really feeling that it is all that hard work. Keap up the good work, you`re doing great.... that`s what she will tell you to keap you going...
